{"tid":729794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過馬路遭的士撞飛 71歲男子重傷昏迷","createTime":"2018-07-05T00:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T02:39:21.000Z","uid":122,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a169a6ce92d693160f33aaffc22843b2e7066e","tid":729794,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T00:58:21.000Z","msg":"旺角彌敦道與登打士街交界，凌晨4時許，一名男子在燈位過馬路時，遭一輛駛經的士撞傷。傷者飛彈上擋風玻璃後反彈墮地，跌在3米外地上。傷者身有酒氣，頭部及手腳受傷昏迷不醒，由救護員送院搶救。警方事後撿獲的士行車記錄片段，帶返警署調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n的士事發時沿彌敦道快線往尖沙嘴行駛，傷者姓雷71歲，由左邊步出馬路。<span style=\"color: blue;\">姓陳(67歲)司機表示，當時行車訊號為綠燈。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180705/58401544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58401544&d=E4v4%2B%2BvUR8WhfjwABT4B48n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5aa6b094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58401544&h=bafceacd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180705/58401544</a>"},{"pid":"afedce03189f6814721d5dcfe3ed261824d0f804","tid":729794,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"的士狗vs醉酒廢老<br />\n呢次明顯錯在廢老"},{"pid":"5b2a715385a6ef4493d4be22e45221f9b1ef71f6","tid":729794,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"下世跑快d"},{"pid":"37e7d0232dde016574bbb03f17ec490ea501668b","tid":729794,"uid":164932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"我以前係賽跑冠軍"},{"pid":"cb9ddc9aab7f930ff15ce0fdd0ba6557e32c1acf","tid":729794,"uid":3023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:25:45.000Z","msg":"咁都飛唔到去街尾, 真失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e55db24abb544549f9fc2c9fd741440a75c18f2","tid":729794,"